How is extreme #poverty one of the main causes of #malnutrition?

Poverty alone does not lead to malnutrition, but it seriously affects the availability, access, and affordability of sufficient amounts of nutritious food for the most vulnerable populations.

text:
What is #malnutrition?

Broadly defined, malnutrition is the result of consuming too little of the right kind of foods, or too much of the wrong kind. Undernutrition is caused by consuming a diet that lacks the necessary nutrients to survive, grow and develop in a healthy manner.
